2. How to Fix Your "Collapsing" Code

For a large codebase, do not just wait for autocomplete. Use these three specific interaction modes:
A. The "Surgeon" (Edit Mode)

If you know roughly where the error is, highlight the code block and press Cmd + I (Mac) or Ctrl + I (Windows).

